<li><a href="/wiki/Help:Categories/zh" class="mw-pt-progress mw-pt-progress--complete" title="Help:分类 (100% translated)" lang="zh" dir="ltr">中文</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Help:Categories/ja" class="mw-pt-progress mw-pt-progress--complete" title="Help:カテゴリ (100% translated)" lang="ja" dir="ltr">日本語</a></li>
